(1482, 197, '_sub_contractor_faq_sub_contractor_faq_question_&_ans_1_question_title', 'field_6049e924becf8'),
(1483, 197, 'sub_contractor_faq_sub_contractor_faq_question_&_ans_1_question_ans', '<h4>Q15- How does the different levels/ types of membership work</h4>\r\nThe membership options are split into bronze silver and gold depending on the work radius you cover, your work experience and your requirements. There is a badge system to help indicate this and the membership plan details are shown on the membership page to help you select the correct plan for you. If you have any queries on this, please use the contact us page and we will advise the best plan for you.'),
(1484, 197, '_sub_contractor_faq_sub_contractor_faq_question_&_ans_1_question_ans', 'field_6049e924becf9'),
