(1587, 199, 'company_faq_company_faq_question_&_ans_1_question_ans', '<h4>Q1- Do we have to pay once we’ve hired someone via the website?</h4>\r\nNo matter how many subcontractors you choose to hire, there are no charges or fees of any kind added to your monthly plan when you have a booking request accepted.\r\n<h4>Q2- How does the different levels/ types of membership work?</h4>\r\nFor Companies, the membership options are split into bronze, silver and gold depending on the work radius you cover/would like to search.\r\n<h4>Q3- Is there a limit on the number of subcontractors we can view and hire?</h4>\r\nThere is no limit to the number of subcontractors we can view or hire. The platform is not simply a directory you are subscribing to access, it’s a live database so from day to day, even minute to mute the results will change depending on subcontractor’s availability and your own search criteria.\r\n<h4>Q4- Can we have multiple devices?</h4>\r\nComing Soon\r\n<h4>Q5- If SCM isn’t working for us are we able to cancel our membership at any time?</h4>\r\nComing Soon'),
